T.query: select e.emp_no,s.from_date, t.title from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no and t.from_date = s.from_date  where e.emp_no > 231013

F.query: select e.emp_no,s.from_date, t.title from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no and t.from_date = s.from_date and t.emp_no = s.salary  where e.emp_no > 231013
select e.emp_no,s.from_date, t.title from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.salary join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no and t.from_date = s.from_date  where e.emp_no > 231013
select e.emp_no,s.from_date, t.title from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no  where e.emp_no > 231013
select e.emp_no,s.from_date, t.title from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no left join titles t on e.emp_no = t.emp_no and t.from_date = s.from_date where e.emp_no > 231013
